0:16:09.939,000 --> 0:16:1,000
we've kept in touch all these years.

334
0:16:12.268,000 --> 0:16:15,000
And he himself has gone on to continue practicing mindfulness

335
0:16:16.011,000 --> 0:16:17,000
in a daily way.

336
0:16:17.748,000 --> 0:16:19,000
He was promoted to major,

337
0:16:20.138,000 --> 0:16:23,000
he actually then ended up retiring from the Marine Corps.

