361
0:17:42.382,000 --> 0:17:44,000
Pay attention to your attention.

362
0:17:45.77,000 --> 0:17:46,000
Alright?

363
0:17:46.957,000 --> 0:17:48,000
Pay attention to your attention

364
0:17:49.284,000 --> 0:17:54,000
and incorporate mindfulness training as part of your daily wellness toolkit,

365
0:17:54.433,000 --> 0:17:57,000
in order to tame your own wandering mind

366
0:17:57.672,000 --> 0:18:,000
and to allow your attention to be a trusted guide in your own life.

367
0:18:01.817,000 --> 0:18:02,000
Thank you.

